    {
        "content": "<p>Note that this would already be enough to define, say, the curvature of a Riemannian manifold (as a bilinear map into the endomorphisms of the tangent space) and to state that this is a smooth map:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">variable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">RiemannianBundle</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Ü¶</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">TangentSpace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">IsContMDiffRiemannianBundle</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚àû</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">EB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Ü¶</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">TangentSpace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">EMetricSpace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">IsRiemannianManifold</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">curvature</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">TangentSpace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">TangentSpace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">TangentSpace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">TangentSpace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">theorem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">contMDiff_curvature</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">ContMDiff</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">IB</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">prod</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ùìò</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">EB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">EB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">EB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">EB</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚àû</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Ü¶</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">TotalSpace</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mk'</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Ü¶</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">TangentSpace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">TangentSpace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">TangentSpace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">TangentSpace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">EB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">EB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">EB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">EB</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">curvature</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
